  "rationale": "<p>The greatest common factor of 8a<sup>7</sup>b\u00b3 and 24a\u00b3b\u00b3 is 8a\u00b3b\u00b3. Factoring out: 8a<sup>7</sup>b\u00b3 = 8a\u00b3b\u00b3 \u00b7 a<sup>4</sup> and 24a\u00b3b\u00b3 = 8a\u00b3b\u00b3 \u00b7 3. So the expression equals 8a\u00b3b\u00b3(a<sup>4</sup> + 3). Choice (d) is correct.</p>",
